---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - White Rabbit WCS"
  description="The story of Phoenix's premier West Coast Swing community. Follow the white rabbit into a world where community comes first."
>
  <main class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1 class="page-title gradient-text">Follow the White Rabbit</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">The Story of Phoenix's Premier WCS Community</p>
      </header>

      <div class="story-content">
        <section class="story-section">
          <div class="section-icon">üêá</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">> The Beginning</h2>
          <p>
            Back in 2018, Phoenix's West Coast Swing scene was stuck. The younger
            dancers wanted modern music and fresh energy, but the established venues
            weren't interested in changing. When COVID restrictions lifted in Arizona,
            we saw our chance.
          </p>
          <p>
            We started throwing speakeasy-style socials in living rooms. Just friends,
            good music, and dancing. At our last home event, someone joked about doing
            guerrilla marketing with bunny stencils and "Follow the White Rabbit" messages
            around town. The name caught on immediately. White Rabbit Society was born.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="story-section">
          <div class="section-icon">üíö</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">> Community First, Always</h2>
          <p>
            White Rabbit isn't about making money. It's about people. We put the
            community first, and everything else falls into place.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every year we survey our dancers. Real voices. Real input. Real change.
            We started with 24 people in a tiny room. Now our monthly socials pull
            130 to 200 dancers. We grew because we actually listen.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our annual Social Dance Champions? Not picked by judges. The community
            votes. Because this is your scene as much as it is ours.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="story-section">
          <div class="section-icon">‚ú®</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">> What Makes Us Different</h2>
          <p>
            There's an African proverb: if you want to go fast, go alone. If you
            want to go far, go together. That's us.
          </p>
          <p>
            We play contemporary music. We create an atmosphere where everyone feels
            welcome, whether you're taking your first steps or you've been dancing
            for years. We run annual surveys and actually implement what people tell us.
            And we're building something special right here in the Valley.
          </p>
          <p>
            Phoenix needed a modern WCS venue that put dancers first. So we built one.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="story-section">
          <div class="section-icon">üåü</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">> The Journey Continues</h2>
          <p>
            From living room socials to Arizona's biggest monthly West Coast Swing
            event. White Rabbit has become more than a dance community. It's a movement.
            A place where the music is modern, the energy is electric, and every dancer
            matters.
          </p>
          <p>
            The white rabbit led us down this path. Now we're inviting you to follow.
          </p>
          <p class="cta-text">
            Ready to see how deep the rabbit hole goes?
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="quote-block">
          <blockquote>
            "If you want to go fast, go alone.<br>
            If you want to go far, go together."
          </blockquote>
          <cite>‚Äî African Proverb</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .story-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .story-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .story-section p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .features-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .features-list li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .features-list li::before {
    content: '‚ñ∏';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .features-list strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .quote-block {
    margin: 4rem 0;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);
    text-align: center;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  cite {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-page {
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }

    .page-header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .story-section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .section-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .story-section p,
    .features-list li {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    blockquote {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .quote-block {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
